msgid "**Defaults to:** `0`"
msgstr "**默认值：** `0`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:20
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.comm.is_fwd_high_precision_reduce_enable`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.comm.is_fwd_high_precision_reduce_enable`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:22
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to enable high-precision (fp32) reduce "
"for partial out during dist-attn forward to trade-off double comm "
"overhead for increased precision and less dtype-cast overhead."
msgstr ""
"将此环境变量设为 `1` 以启用 dist-attn 前向传播中 partial out "
"的高精度（fp32）reduce，以双倍通信开销换取更高精度和更少的 dtype 转换开销。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:26
msgid ""
"Inside the ffa forward kernel, we always use high-precision (fp32) "
"accumulation for partial out."
msgstr "在 ffa 前向内核内部，我们始终对 partial out 使用高精度（fp32）累加。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:28
msgid "We always use high-precision (fp32) lse everywhere."
msgstr "我们在所有地方始终使用高精度（fp32）的 lse。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:30
msgid "This feature works for out only when enabling qo comm."
msgstr "此功能仅在启用 qo comm 时对 out 生效。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:34
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_BACKWARD_HIGH_PRECISION_REDUCE**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_BACKWARD_HIGH_PRECISION_REDUCE**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:37
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.comm.is_bwd_high_precision_reduce_enable`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.comm.is_bwd_high_precision_reduce_enable`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:39
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to enable high-precision (fp32) reduce "
"for partial dq,dk,dv during dist-attn backward to trade-off double comm "
"overhead for increased precision and less dtype-cast overhead."
msgstr ""
"将此环境变量设为 `1` 以启用 dist-attn 反向传播中 partial dq,dk,dv "
"的高精度（fp32）reduce，以双倍通信开销换取更高精度和更少的 dtype 转换开销。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:43
msgid ""
"Inside the ffa backward kernel, we always use high-precision (fp32) "
"accumulation for partial dq,dk,dv."
msgstr "在 ffa 反向内核内部，我们始终对 partial dq,dk,dv 使用高精度（fp32）累加。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:45
msgid "This feature works for dq only when enabling qo comm."
msgstr "此功能仅在启用 qo comm 时对 dq 生效。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:49
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_DSINK_ALL_REDUCE_OP**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_DSINK_ALL_REDUCE_OP**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:51
msgid "**Defaults to:** `none` (options: `none`, `sum`, `avg`)"
msgstr "**默认值：** `none`（可选值：`none`、`sum`、`avg`）"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:52
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.comm.dsink_all_reduce_op`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.comm.dsink_all_reduce_op`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:54
msgid ""
"Set the value of this env variable to control the all-reduce op for sink "
"gradients within `dist_attn_func` when involving attention sink."
msgstr "设置此环境变量的值以控制涉及 attention sink 时 `dist_attn_func` 中 sink 梯度的 all-reduce 操作。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:58
msgid ""
"For now we only accept global replicated sink tensor as input to feed "
"into `dist_attn_func`, and the gradients of sink in each cp rank are "
"partial and requires to be sum-reduced across cp ranks."
msgstr ""
"目前我们仅接受全局复制的 sink 张量作为输入传入 `dist_attn_func`，每个 cp rank 中的 sink 梯度是部分的，需要在"
" cp rank 之间进行 sum-reduce。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:60
msgid ""
"However, since sink tensor is learnable, it will be considered as a "
"regular parameter in the model similar to `bias` in `nn.Linear` layer."
msgstr "然而，由于 sink 张量是可学习的，它将被视为模型中的常规参数，类似于 `nn.Linear` 层中的 `bias`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:62
msgid ""
"So under some popular training frameworks, such as Megatron-LM, FSDP, the"
" sum-reduction across cp ranks of the partial gradients of sink might be "
"automatically applied within the whole `dp x cp` mesh."
msgstr ""
"因此在一些流行的训练框架（如 Megatron-LM、FSDP）中，sink 部分梯度在 cp rank 之间的 sum-reduction "
"可能会在整个 `dp x cp` mesh 中自动执行。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:64
msgid ""
"To avoid repeated reduction, we provide this environment variable to "
"specify the all-reduce op for sink gradients within `dist_attn_func`, "
"whose default value is `none` to NOT apply any reduction to sink "
"gradients by `dist_attn_func` and let the framework handle it."
msgstr ""
"为避免重复 reduction，我们提供此环境变量来指定 `dist_attn_func` 中 sink 梯度的 all-reduce "
"操作，其默认值为 `none`，即 `dist_attn_func` 不对 sink 梯度执行任何 reduction，而由框架来处理。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:66
msgid ""
"However, under the scenarios w/o any framework mechanism to reduce "
"parameters across cp ranks, you have to specify this environment variable"
" to `sum`."
msgstr "但在没有任何框架机制来跨 cp rank reduce 参数的场景下，您必须将此环境变量设为 `sum`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:68
msgid ""
"And sometimes, `avg` might also be an option when you need to scale the "
"sink gradients by `1/cp`."
msgstr "有时 `avg` 也是一个选项，当您需要将 sink 梯度按 `1/cp` 缩放时可以使用。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:72
msgid "For Runtime"
msgstr "运行时相关"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:74
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_LOG_LEVEL**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_LOG_LEVEL**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:76
msgid "**Defaults to:** `WARN`"
msgstr "**默认值：** `WARN`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:77
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.general.log_level`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.general.log_level`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:79
msgid ""
"Set this env variable to control the logging verbosity of the entire "
"`magi_attention` package. Valid values (case-insensitive) are `DEBUG`, "
"`INFO`, `WARN`, `WARNING`, `ERROR`, `CRITICAL`."
msgstr ""
"设置此环境变量以控制整个 `magi_attention` 包的日志详细程度。有效值（不区分大小写）为 "
"`DEBUG`、`INFO`、`WARN`、`WARNING`、`ERROR`、`CRITICAL`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:82
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_KERNEL_BACKEND**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_KERNEL_BACKEND**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:84
msgid "**Defaults to:** `ffa`"
msgstr "**默认值：** `ffa`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:85
#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:200
#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:357
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.general.kernel_backend`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.general.kernel_backend`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:87
msgid "Set this env variable to choose the attn kernel backend. Valid values are:"
msgstr "设置此环境变量以选择注意力内核后端。有效值为："

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:89
msgid "`ffa`: flex-flash-attention (default, high-performance persistent kernel)."
msgstr "`ffa`：flex-flash-attention（默认，高性能持久化内核）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:90
msgid ""
"`sdpa`: offline SDPA implementation (for testing / high precision like "
"`fp32`/`fp64`)."
msgstr "`sdpa`：离线 SDPA 实现（用于测试 / `fp32`、`fp64` 等高精度）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:91
msgid ""
"`sdpa_ol`: online (block-wise) SDPA implementation (for testing, lower "
"memory than `sdpa`)."
msgstr "`sdpa_ol`：在线（分块）SDPA 实现（用于测试，显存占用低于 `sdpa`）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:92
msgid "`fa4`: Flash-Attention 4 monkey-patch (workaround for Blackwell GPUs)."
msgstr "`fa4`：Flash-Attention 4 monkey patch（Blackwell GPU 的临时方案）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:95
msgid ""
"This supersedes the legacy `MAGI_ATTENTION_SDPA_BACKEND=1` and "
"`MAGI_ATTENTION_FA4_BACKEND=1` toggles, which are still supported but "
"must NOT be set together with `MAGI_ATTENTION_KERNEL_BACKEND`."
msgstr ""
"此变量取代了旧的 `MAGI_ATTENTION_SDPA_BACKEND=1` 和 `MAGI_ATTENTION_FA4_BACKEND=1`"
" 开关，后者仍受支持，但不得与 `MAGI_ATTENTION_KERNEL_BACKEND` 同时设置。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:99
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_PRECISION**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_PRECISION**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:101
msgid "**Defaults to:** unset (use the input dtype as-is)"
msgstr "**默认值：** 未设置（保持输入 dtype 不变）"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:102
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.general.precision`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.general.precision`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:104
msgid ""
"Set this env variable to override the compute dtype for attention "
"kernels. Valid values are `bf16`, `fp16`, `fp32`, `fp64`. When set, input"
" Q/K/V are cast to the specified dtype before attention computation, and "
"the output is cast back to the original input dtype."
msgstr ""
"设置此环境变量以覆盖注意力内核的计算 dtype。有效值为 `bf16`、`fp16`、`fp32`、`fp64`。设置后，输入 Q/K/V "
"会在注意力计算前转换为指定 dtype，输出再转换回原始输入 dtype。"

