#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:221
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_QO_COMM**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_QO_COMM**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:224
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.comm.is_qo_comm_enable`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.comm.is_qo_comm_enable`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:226
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to enable query/output communication, "
"including fetching remote q (fwd), reducing partial out and lse (fwd), "
"fetching remote q,o,lse,do (bwd), reducing partial dq (bwd), to eliminate"
" the restriction that communication is limited solely to key/value."
msgstr ""
"将此环境变量设为 `1` 以启用 query/output 通信，包括获取远程 q（前向）、reduce partial out 和 "
"lse（前向）、获取远程 q,o,lse,do（反向）、reduce partial dq（反向），以消除通信仅限于 key/value 的限制。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:233
