"settings by concatenating multiple Q heads sharing the same KV head."
msgstr ""
"将此环境变量设为 ``1`` 以启用 flex-flash-attention 反向的 CatGQA 模式，通过拼接共享相同 KV head "
"的多个 Q head 来进一步优化 GQA 设置下的性能。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:270
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_BWD_HIDE_TAIL_REDUCE**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_BWD_HIDE_TAIL_REDUCE**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:273
msgid ""
"**Used by:** "
"`magi_attention.env.general.dist_attn_backward_hide_tail_reduce`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.general.dist_attn_backward_hide_tail_reduce`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:275
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to trade saving the last remote `kv` "
"activation for reordering overlap stages during backward, hiding the "
"final remote `group_reduce` with the host FFA stage."
msgstr ""
"将此环境变量设为 ``1`` 以牺牲保存最后一个远程 `kv` 激活来重排反向传播中的重叠阶段，将最终的远程 `group_reduce` "
"隐藏在主机 FFA 阶段中。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:278
msgid ""
"This feature is experimental and under active development for now, and "
"not compatible with many other features like qo comm, thus please do NOT "
"enable it unless you know exactly what you are doing."
msgstr "此功能目前处于实验阶段并在积极开发中，与许多其他功能（如 qo comm）不兼容，因此请不要启用，除非您清楚了解其影响。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:282
