msgstr "**默认值：** 当 `CUDA_DEVICE_MAX_CONNECTIONS` > `1` 时为 `4`，否则为 `0`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:292
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.comm.ffa_fwd_sm_margin_save_for_comm`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.comm.ffa_fwd_sm_margin_save_for_comm`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:294
msgid ""
"Set the value of this env variable to control the number of SMs of the "
"ffa forward kernel saved for comm kernels."
msgstr "设置此环境变量的值以控制 ffa 前向内核为通信内核预留的 SM 数量。"

