msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FFA_BACKWARD_SM_MARGIN**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:299
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.comm.ffa_bwd_sm_margin_save_for_comm`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.comm.ffa_bwd_sm_margin_save_for_comm`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:301
msgid ""
"Set the value of this env variable to control the number of SMs of the "
"ffa backward kernel saved for comm kernels."
msgstr "设置此环境变量的值以控制 ffa 反向内核为通信内核预留的 SM 数量。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:303
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_CPP_BACKEND**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_CPP_BACKEND**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:306
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.env.general.is_cpp_backend_enable`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.env.general.is_cpp_backend_enable`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:308
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to enable C++ backend for core data "
"structures (`AttnRange`, `AttnMaskType`, etc.) to avoid Python overhead."
msgstr ""
"将此环境变量设为 `1` 以启用核心数据结构（`AttnRange`、`AttnMaskType` 等）的 C++ 后端，以避免 Python "
"开销。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:311
msgid ""
"This feature is experimental and under active development for now. If the"
" C++ extension is not found or this variable is set to `0`, it will fall "
"back to the Python implementation."
msgstr "此功能目前处于实验阶段并在积极开发中。如果未找到 C++ 扩展或此变量设为 `0`，将回退到 Python 实现。"

