msgstr "**默认值：** `ceil(num_cpu_cores * 0.9)`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:486
msgid ""
"Set the value of this env variable to control the number of parallel "
"compilation jobs used to pre-build ffa kernels."
msgstr "设置此环境变量的值以控制预构建 ffa 内核时使用的并行编译任务数。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:488
msgid "**MAX_JOBS**"
msgstr "**MAX_JOBS**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:493
msgid ""
"Set the value of this env variable to control the number of parallel "
"compilation jobs used to build the extension modules other than ffa."
msgstr "设置此环境变量的值以控制构建 ffa 以外的扩展模块时使用的并行编译任务数。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:495
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_PREBUILD_FFA**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_PREBUILD_FFA**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:497
#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:579
msgid "**Defaults to:** `1`"
msgstr "**默认值：** `1`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:500
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to enable pre-build ffa kernels for some "
"common options with `ref_block_size=None` and leave others built in jit "
"mode."
msgstr "将此环境变量设为 `1` 以启用对一些 `ref_block_size=None` 的常见选项预构建 ffa 内核，其余选项则以 JIT 模式构建。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:502
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_SKIP_CUDA_BUILD**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_SKIP_CUDA_BUILD**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:507
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to skip building all the CUDA extension "
"modules entirely (e.g. for a Python-only / docs build)."
msgstr "将此环境变量设为 `1` 以完全跳过构建所有 CUDA 扩展模块（例如仅 Python / 文档构建时）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:509
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_SKIP_MAGI_ATTN_EXT_BUILD**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_SKIP_MAGI_ATTN_EXT_BUILD**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:514
msgid "Toggle this env variable to `1` can skip building `magi_attn_ext`."
msgstr "将此环境变量设为 `1` 可跳过构建 `magi_attn_ext`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:516
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_SKIP_MAGI_ATTN_COMM_BUILD**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_SKIP_MAGI_ATTN_COMM_BUILD**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:521
msgid "Toggle this env variable to `1` can skip building `magi_attn_comm`."
msgstr "将此环境变量设为 `1` 可跳过构建 `magi_attn_comm`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:523
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FORCE_CXX11_ABI**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FORCE_CXX11_ABI**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:528
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to force building the extension modules "
"with the C++11 ABI (`_GLIBCXX_USE_CXX11_ABI=1`), to match a PyTorch build"
" compiled with the new ABI."
msgstr ""
"将此环境变量设为 `1` 以强制使用 C++11 ABI（`_GLIBCXX_USE_CXX11_ABI=1`）构建扩展模块，以匹配使用新 ABI"
" 编译的 PyTorch。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:530
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_DISABLE_SM90_FEATURES**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_DISABLE_SM90_FEATURES**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:535
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to disable the SM90 (Hopper)-specific "
"features when building the extension modules, e.g. when targeting a "
"toolchain without SM90 support."
msgstr "将此环境变量设为 `1` 以在构建扩展模块时禁用 SM90（Hopper）专属特性，例如面向不支持 SM90 的工具链时。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:537
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FFA_FA4_CACHE_DIR**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FFA_FA4_CACHE_DIR**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:539
msgid "**Defaults to:** `magi_attention/lib/ffa_fa4_cache/`"
msgstr "**默认值：** `magi_attention/lib/ffa_fa4_cache/`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:540
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.functional.fa4_utils`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.functional.fa4_utils`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:542
msgid ""
"Set this env variable to specify the cache directory for pre-compiled "
"`FFA_FA4` kernels."
msgstr "设置此环境变量以指定预编译 `FFA_FA4` 内核的缓存目录。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:544
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_BUILD_COMPUTE_CAPABILITY**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_BUILD_COMPUTE_CAPABILITY**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:546
msgid "**Defaults to:** unset (auto-detect the current GPU device)"
msgstr "**默认值：** 未设置（自动检测当前 GPU 设备）"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:549
msgid ""
"Set this env variable to specify the compute capability used to build "
"MagiAttention extension modules (affects `magi_attn_comm` and "
"`create_block_mask`). Supports comma-separated values for multi-arch "
"builds, e.g. `MAGI_ATTENTION_BUILD_COMPUTE_CAPABILITY=90,100`. If not "
"set, we will try to detect the compute capability of the current GPU "
"device, and raise an error if detection fails."
msgstr ""
"设置此环境变量以指定构建 MagiAttention 扩展模块时使用的计算能力（影响 `magi_attn_comm` 和 "
"`create_block_mask`）。支持逗号分隔的多架构值，例如 "
"`MAGI_ATTENTION_BUILD_COMPUTE_CAPABILITY=90,100`。如果未设置，我们将尝试检测当前 GPU "
"设备的计算能力。如果检测失败将抛出错误。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:551
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_ALLOW_BUILD_WITH_CUDA12**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_ALLOW_BUILD_WITH_CUDA12**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:556
msgid ""
"Set this env variable to `1` to allow building MagiAttention extension "
"modules with `CUDA-12`, which might cause significant performance "
"degradation compared to `CUDA-13+`. When `0`, we will raise an error and "
"abort the installation if the CUDA version is lower than `13.0`."
msgstr ""
"将此环境变量设为 `1` 以允许使用 `CUDA-12` 构建 MagiAttention 扩展模块，这可能导致与 `CUDA-13+` "
"相比显著的性能下降。当为 `0` 时，如果 CUDA 版本低于 `13.0`，我们将抛出错误并中止安装。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:558
msgid "**NVSHMEM_DIR**"
msgstr "**NVSHMEM_DIR**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:560
msgid ""
"**Defaults to:** the system module `nvidia-nvshmem-cu12` (as listed in "
"`requirements.txt`)"
msgstr "**默认值：** 系统模块 `nvidia-nvshmem-cu12`（如 `requirements.txt` 中所列）"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:563
msgid ""
"Set this env variable to the path of the custom `nvshmem` installation "
"directory."
msgstr "设置此环境变量为自定义 `nvshmem` 安装目录的路径。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:565
msgid ""
"If not found anywhere, all relative features used in native group "
"collective comm kernels are disabled."
msgstr "如果在任何位置都未找到，native group collective 通信内核中的所有相关功能将被禁用。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:568
msgid "For Testing"
msgstr "测试相关"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:570
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_PARAMETERIZE_RUN_IN_MP**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_PARAMETERIZE_RUN_IN_MP**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:573
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.testing` (`with_run_in_mp`)"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.testing` (`with_run_in_mp`)"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:575
msgid ""
"Whether to run parameterized distributed test cases in a multiprocessing "
"context. This is set internally by the `@with_run_in_mp` decorator rather"
" than being configured by users directly."
msgstr "是否在多进程上下文中运行参数化的分布式测试用例。此变量由 `@with_run_in_mp` 装饰器内部设置，而非由用户直接配置。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:577
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_TEST_PRINT_NO_MISMATCH**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_TEST_PRINT_NO_MISMATCH**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:580
msgid "**Used by:** `magi_attention.testing` (`assert_close`)"
msgstr "**使用方：** `magi_attention.testing` (`assert_close`)"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:582
msgid ""
"Whether to print the \"has no mismatch\" message when two tensors match "
"in `assert_close`. Set to `0` to disable it, mainly used to reduce "
"logging noise in CI."
msgstr ""
"当两个张量在 `assert_close` 中匹配时，是否打印 “has no mismatch” 消息。设为 `0` 可禁用它，主要用于减少 "
"CI 中的日志噪声。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:584
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_COPYRIGHT_TEST_YEAR**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_COPYRIGHT_TEST_YEAR**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:586
msgid "**Defaults to:** current calendar year"
msgstr "**默认值：** 当前日历年份"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:587
msgid "**Used by:** `tools/codestyle/copyright.py`"
msgstr "**使用方：** `tools/codestyle/copyright.py`"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:589
msgid ""
"Overrides the \"current year\" used by the copyright-header check. Useful"
" for reproducible testing of the copyright tooling."
msgstr "覆盖版权头检查所使用的“当前年份”。用于对版权工具进行可复现的测试。"
